        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Chittersnap looses a gout of sticky web at one creature within 30 feet (@Check[type:reflex|dc:21]). On a failure the target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.eIcWbB5o3pP6OIMe]{Immobilized} (Escape or @Check[type:athletics|dc:21] to break free; @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.kWc1fhmv9LBiTuei]{Grabbed} only on a critical failure).</p>"
