        "actions": {
          "value": null
        },
        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A creature damaged by Chittersnap's Jaws is exposed to its venom: @Check[type:fortitude|dc:23], a 1-stage poison dealing @Damage[1d6[poison]] and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled 2} for 1 round (4 rounds on a critical failure).</p>"
        },
