        },
        "actions": {
          "value": null
        },
        "category": "defensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Chittersnap commands every spider on Eel's End — the true source of Devargo's 'control.' While it lives, the dream spiders and giant spider act on its initiative. If it dies, all of them revert to feral hunting, attacking the nearest creature (Devargo included).</p>"
        },
